name: Lets Take Over The Universe
blurb: Want to help a Soldier in a pink chicken suit, a broken robot, a little man in a big ship and a very lost lady take over the universe?

rewards.reward: Merchant Class:\r\nHave your name immortalized in video game history! Your Name will be added to a "Special Thanks" Section of the credits on both the game and the website.

Explorer Class:\r\nHave your name immortalized in video game history! Your Name will be added to a "Special Thanks" Section of the credits.\r\nYou also get a copy of the game on the platform of your choice!

Patrolship Class:\r\nSee the game come to life before its released, with behind-the-scenes stories, concept art and storyboards on the Development Blog!\r\nYou will also get a special "Thanks" in the credits and a copy of the game!
Corvette Class:\r\nGet a copy of the game on the platform of your choice\r\nAND an Exclusive T-Shirt!
Be-An-Extra Edition: Send us a Photo, We will Draw you as a Character and add you to the game as a random ship pilot! As well as a copy of the game on the platform of your choice!
Collectors Edition:\r\nEverything from the Previous Ranks!\r\nGet the Shirt, The Dev Blog, Name in the credits, Be an extra and get a copy of the game!

"Unique" Edition:
Design a Unique Unit that will appear randomly floating around the universe!
This deal grants you the ability to choose the ship type, faction (pirate, trader, military), the ships name, the pilots name, provide a photo and our artists will redraw you as the ships captain! You can also write your characters "flavor text" (with seperate guidelines)!
 As well as a copy of the game on the platform of your choice!

Battleship Class: 
Design a Quest!
Sick of the old "Go here, do this" quests...
Well for $200 you can finally do something about it! Get the opportunity to have a Skype meeting (up to 30min) with the games Creator and lead Designer! Almost anything with-in the scope of engine (and not too offensive) could happen!
You will have the opportunity to discuss game content, previous mission designs and concepts via email prior to the Meeting.
You also get a copy of the game on the platform of your choice!

Super Carrier Class: Design a Solar System! You get to choose a Name for the Planet, You can help write the planets description, choose a government type, write a character (and provide a photo to our the artists) for your quest giver and design a quest chain for your system...what?! Thats right, for only $300 you get the opportunity to have a Skype meeting (up to 2 hours) with the games Creator and lead Designer! Almost anything with-in the scope of engine (and not too offensive) could happen! You will have the opportunity to discuss game content, previous mission designs and concepts via email prior to the Meeting. You also get a copy of the game on the platform of your choice!

The Combo:\r\nEverything from The Super Carrier Class, the Battle Ship Class and the "Unique" Edition! With the added feature... Your Unique Unit will have a place to call home and will no longer be a random unit in the game!\r\nYou can visit your Solar System anytime and pay your buddy a visit in your own copy of the game as well!

Supporting Cast Edition:
You can help create a character that can join the players party!
The game has 4 "escort" characters already but why stop there? If you have always wanted to "Get in the Game", this is a chance for you to do so, literally!
With this level of support, you will get to choose from a collection of unique ship models, the ships name, the pilots name, the ships special weapon and the characters "flavor text" used in conversation. You can provide a photo or take part in the creative direction of the characters art!
You also get to help design a quest that will end with your character joining the players party!
To bad there is no "Best Supporting Character" award!
The New Guy:\r\nHonorary co-producer listing in the game credits. (The title co-producer will be in name only.) \r\nYou also get everything from "The Combo" rank!
